{"tid":2349531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2021年元旦日鄭文傑為影子議會拍左段好詳細嘅Q&A片","createTime":"2021-01-01T15:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T12:41:54.000Z","uid":164837,"like":86,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"39fd0ac5dcdd9c4e9c60529bd783a5bfde361f25","tid":2349531,"uid":164837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T15:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0KdjMxp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0KdjMxp.jpg&h=b16c3be2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nYouTube:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=izBfPoewtuc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DizBfPoewtuc&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=c37183ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=izBfPoewtuc</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKshadowparliament/posts/152382016648249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKshadowparliament%2Fposts%2F152382016648249&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=10a87c21\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKshadowparliament/posts/152382016648249</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKShadowParl/status/1345026930446393346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKShadowParl%2Fstatus%2F1345026930446393346&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=7d3fc142\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKShadowParl%2Fstatus%2F1345026930446393346&h=028d7e00\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HKShadowParl/status/1345026930446393346</a><br />\n<br />\nIG:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CJgdzUogoV4/?igshid=97j0iics9240\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCJgdzUogoV4%2F%3Figshid%3D97j0iics9240&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=4097ae24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCJgdzUogoV4%2F%3Figshid%3D97j0iics9240&h=d4bab8b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CJgdzUogoV4/?igshid=97j0iics9240</a><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n時間軸 Timestamp:<br />\n<br />\n00:47: 為什麼要成立香港影子議會呢？ Why did we set up the Hong Kong Shadow Parliament (HKSP)?<br />\n<br />\n02:01: 香港影子議會有何功能呢？What are the functions of the Hong Kong Shadow Parliament?<br />\n<br />\n02:51: 香港影子議會是「流亡議會／流亡政府」嗎？ Is the Hong Kong Shadow Parliament a parliament or government in exile?<br />\n<br />\n05:35: 香港影子議會是「大台」嗎？ Is the HKSP attempting to play a role of a &ldquo;leading stage&rdquo;?<br />\n<br />\n07:19: 香港影子議會是否宣揚「港獨」？ Is the Hong Kong Shadow Parliament advocating Hong Kong independence?<br />\n<br />\n08:55: 誰可參與香港影子議會，有甚麼資格？Who can participate HKSP? What is the eligibility?<br />\n<br />\n10:38: 誰可以於香港影子議會內投票呢？Who can vote at HKSP?<br />\n<br />\n10:53: 香港影子議會於甚麼地方舉行？Where will the HKSP be held?<br />\n<br />\n12:33: 投票的形式是甚麼？What is the form of the voting within HKSP?<br />\n<br />\n13:50: 怎樣能夠保障選民的安全呢？How do we guarantee voters&rsquo; safety?<br />\n<br />\n15:29: 香港影子議會公眾諮詢有甚麼目的？What are the purposes of the HKSP Public Consultation?<br />\n<br />\n16:26 公眾諮詢的時間有多長？What is the duration of the public consultation period?<br />\n<br />\n18:26 香港影子議會的結構是怎樣組成呢？What is the structure of HKSP and how it is constituted?<br />\n<br />\n23:46 香港影子議會與「國際戰線」有何關係呢？<br />\nWhat is the relationship between the HKSP and the &ldquo;International Front&rdquo;?<br />\n<br />\n23:04 結語Ending"},{"pid":"90fa983cf29890e28bb7d4d43672c981d48ddbf4","tid":2349531,"uid":51754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T15:33:00.000Z","msg":"[求推] 衞生署 強制檢測名單 又双叒叕有錯？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2349363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2349363</a>"},{"pid":"f7664c208a7f3afedecf2b3fbd9240bce3d92312","tid":2349531,"